<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ram hlapi ah Pathian bia lomi tampi, Thlarau rel cawk lo kha an tlau
 lan lai, Hodah kal lai, Khamhnak kong kha chim awkah, Jesuh zoh i harnak
 kha ruat loin.

[C1]
   &quot;Nawl-ngeihnak a ka pek dih cang Nawl ngeihnak a ka pek dih cang,
   Ram kip ah kal in Thawngtha bia chim hna u; Nan sinah ka um zungzal lai,&quot;
   a ti.

[V2]
 Zohhmanh, vawlei khua zakip in an in sawm, Khrih ralkap hna, Tho u law
 lut tuah u, Khrihfa tho u, Lungkhat tein dir tuah u, Thawngtha bia in
 sualnak cikcin chat u.

[C2]
   &quot;Nawl-ngeihnak a ka pek dih cang Nawl ngeihnak a ka pek dih cang,
   Ram kip ah kal in Thawngtha bia chim hna u; Nan sinah ka um zungzal lai,&quot;
   a ti.

[V3]
 &quot;Zeica'h dah nan thih lai,&quot; Pathian nih a ti, &quot;Zeica'h dah nan thih
 lai&quot; tiah au chin ve, Thihnak tihnung tei awkah Jesuh a thi, Nunnak le
 khamhnak cu aupi cio u.

[C3]
   &quot;Nawl-ngeihnak a ka pek dih cang Nawl ngeihnak a ka pek dih cang,
   Ram kip ah kal in Thawngtha bia chim hna u; Nan sinah ka um zungzal lai,&quot;
   a ti.

[V4]
 &quot;Pathian thangthat siseh,&quot; tiah phun kip chungin, Hla-saknak kha
 khulrang in tlunter tuah, &quot;Hal-le-lu-jah! Bawipa cu kan Siangpahrang,&quot;
 Tiin khamhmi vialte cu an au lai.

[C4]
   &quot;Nawl-ngeihnak a ka pek dih cang Nawl ngeihnak a ka pek dih cang,
   Ram kip ah kal in Thawngtha bia chim hna u; Nan sinah ka um zungzal lai,&quot;
   a ti.</lyrics>
